      "text": "Road trip game akin to [Keep Driving](https://store.steampowered.com/app/2756920/Keep_Driving) (maybe more supernatural with [Pacific Drive](https://store.steampowered.com/app/1458140/Pacific_Drive/)?). Keep it homey (around Niagara)?\n\nMechanics:\n- Resource management\n\t- Fuel\n\t- Food/Water\n\t- People?\n\t- Sleep/Energy\n- A core mechanic between stops\n\t- Keep Driving does \"card battles\"\n- Postcards between towns\n\nFeatures:\n- A story about someone\n\t- driving away from something\n\t- to something\n- A radio\n- Car upgrades\n- Requests\n- Crank to pedal (accelerate/brake)\n- Different car types (pros/cons)",
